				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/H%C3%AD-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Xu-Ng%C3%B4n-th%E1%BA%A3o-c%C3%A1c-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-1xg3hi80FKcKoSCSEece2g">Hí đề Xu Ngôn thảo các tam thập nhị vận - 戲題樞言草閣三十二韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Ho%E1%BA%A1-lang-trung-M%E1%BA%B7c-Si-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-d%E1%BA%A1-v%C5%A9-b%E1%BA%A5t-m%E1%BB%8B-%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-b%C3%A1o/poem-sDm1mVKun2Gcx4ztJ-BafA">Hoạ lang trung Mặc Si tiên sinh dạ vũ bất mị độc báo - 和郎中墨癡先生夜雨不寐讀報感作原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%E1%BB%93-trung-t%E1%BB%91ng-K%C3%ADnh-th%E1%BA%ADp-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-th%C3%ADch-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-L%C4%83ng/poem-mrpQ-77uEcTVKP1NRq8SDg">Hồ trung tống Kính thập sứ quân thích Quảng Lăng - 湖中送敬十使君適廣陵</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/L%E1%BB%87-nh%C3%A2n-h%C3%A0nh/poem-7LVazFkRs_J0V_ANEMXKdQ">Lệ nhân hành - 麗人行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-V%C4%83n-Tr%E1%BB%A9/Quy-thi%E1%BB%81n/poem-sdfenHuWQEpwob11JR_IHw">Quy thiền - 歸禪</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-V%C4%83n-Tr%E1%BB%A9/author-xpAnCf3fVJwFMTuePXmYuw">Trần Văn Trứ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/T%E1%BA%B7ng-b%E1%BA%A3n-huy%E1%BB%87n-hu%E1%BA%A5n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-Trang-Li%E1%BB%87t-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-th%C4%83ng-bi%C3%AAn-tu-sung-gi%E1%BA%A3ng-t%E1%BA%ADp/poem-m-Dj2kroUbeo4b45J0W2iQ">Tặng bản huyện huấn đạo Trang Liệt Nguyễn thăng biên tu sung giảng tập - 贈本縣訓導莊烈阮升編修充講習</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%9Bi-Ph%E1%BB%A5c-C%E1%BB%95/T%E1%BA%A7n-ch%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-Ho%C3%A0i-h%C3%A0-thu%E1%BB%B7/poem-c0wSihPS8c-X5AeY_qWvrw">Tần chước Hoài hà thuỷ - 頻酌淮河水</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%9Bi-Ph%E1%BB%A5c-C%E1%BB%95/author-fmo28PNwjKb5s2uj6R9_ZA">Đới Phục Cổ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-Hi%E1%BB%87u/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Can-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-l51svDKk5wrQS0vZjVF3yQ">Trường Can hành kỳ 4 - 長干行其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-Hi%E1%BB%87u/author-MRkAoTgdrsRPtV8a7n8AAw">Thôi Hiệu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%A9-t%C3%B9ng/poem-gGXMjqTTUrdwriPEB0cMQw">Tứ tùng - 四松</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-IX/poem-0Z33mbgWOeXVu67Ul0ynXw">Vô đề (IX) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-VNhahLxtqyIrLeDASL0s9Q">Thực Hiền</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
